John Sutton Jr was just 8 years old when his father brought him to his first Kentucky Derby in 1940 . 
  He has attended every race since then and has collected a program from every one . 
  Churchill Downs is inviting him to attend his 76th-straight race as a special guest on May 2 . 
  Sutton was invited to his home to show off his collection of racing memorabilia . 
 